  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0baa\u0baf - \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The problem cannot be resolved by keeping President Gotabaya and Prime Minister Ranil in office - Champika",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "No problem can be solved by keeping President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe in office.",
        "MP Patali Sambika Ranavaka, leader of the 43rd Brigade, said that the role of the People's Liberation Front is important in establishing the All Party-led government.",
        "A meeting between People's Liberation Front leader Anura Kumara Dissanayake, Sunil Atunethi, and members of the 43rd Battalion (11) took place in Colombo.",
        "The Rajapaksas alone have to be held responsible for the country facing a massive economic and political crisis. The weak administration of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has put the entire country in crisis.",
        "If President Gotabaya Rajapaksa had respected the aspirations of the people of the country and stepped down properly, the current crisis would not have emerged.",
        "No problem can be solved by keeping President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe in office.",
        "The draft of the 22nd Amendment to the Constitution which has been approved by the Cabinet cannot be fully accepted.",
        "The people of the country are insisting that the President-Prime Minister should step down. Regarding the government led by the All-Party, attention has been paid to the formation of an interim government by receiving ideas from various parties.",
        "An interim government should be formed if the economic and political crisis is to be resolved."
      ],
